  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>MAKE SURE TO WISHLIST SCIENCE SIMULATOR!</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/e06cd461ee9bef9a8c304d0e3ea7d49a.poster.avif?t=1756989240\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/e06cd461ee9bef9a8c304d0e3ea7d49a.webm?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/e06cd461ee9bef9a8c304d0e3ea7d49a.mp4?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Science Simulator is a experimental video game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > This game was made to inspire the next Leonardo Da Vinci or Marie Currie into Science, Technology, Engineering, Art and Maths (STEAM).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Periodic Table Of Elements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/96d085a935cc6b78a183a7c056e33dbf.poster.avif?t=1756989240\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/96d085a935cc6b78a183a7c056e33dbf.webm?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/96d085a935cc6b78a183a7c056e33dbf.mp4?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Titan and Europa exploration using rovers, (Final update Next) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/d2e1972c117c3d8660942e278967be5f.poster.avif?t=1756989240\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/d2e1972c117c3d8660942e278967be5f.webm?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/d2e1972c117c3d8660942e278967be5f.mp4?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solar System</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/5cd6f37836c58749670da25f0d79f504.poster.avif?t=1756989240\" width=600 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/5cd6f37836c58749670da25f0d79f504.webm?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/5cd6f37836c58749670da25f0d79f504.mp4?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spacecrafts </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/4b2eced9bc4b7940cd3254368dbf22bd.poster.avif?t=1756989240\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/4b2eced9bc4b7940cd3254368dbf22bd.webm?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/4b2eced9bc4b7940cd3254368dbf22bd.mp4?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cosmetics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/42f631ccc6bcf050d54d4086b6cde0d9.poster.avif?t=1756989240\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/42f631ccc6bcf050d54d4086b6cde0d9.webm?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/42f631ccc6bcf050d54d4086b6cde0d9.mp4?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Standard Model Of Physics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/82253ce42544e2a1b2e09639255c301e.poster.avif?t=1756989240\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/82253ce42544e2a1b2e09639255c301e.webm?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/82253ce42544e2a1b2e09639255c301e.mp4?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Marie Curie, Ada Lovelace, Nikola Tesla<strong>,</strong> James Clerk Maxwell, Charles Darwin, Leonardo Da Vinci, Bertrand Russell, Alexander Bell, John Mitchell, Galileo Galilei, Nicolaus Copernicus and Issac Newton</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/c35749fffadf09c77544de71a795dc38.poster.avif?t=1756989240\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/c35749fffadf09c77544de71a795dc38.webm?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/c35749fffadf09c77544de71a795dc38.mp4?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Logic Gates</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/6a4e62e0406ea225146111f3ea412c79.poster.avif?t=1756989240\" width=600 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/6a4e62e0406ea225146111f3ea412c79.webm?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893910/extras/6a4e62e0406ea225146111f3ea412c79.mp4?t=1756989240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solar System Exploration (Final update Next) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Widescreen Support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Virtual Reality Support (VR controlls Planned)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Xbox and Playstation Gamepad compatible (Final update Next)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Deck compatibility (Final update Next for controlls)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and much more planned such as, The Moon, Mars, Enceladous, and Ganymede rover missions, Multiplayer/Co-op. Achivements </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is made by a solo developer, making my first game, using the Cryengine. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I dont remove what im currently working on from the game, for time saving reasons, so you may come across features that are non or semi working that are still in development. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
